---

## âš™ï¸ Main API

### `AICritic(model, X, y)`

* `model`: scikit-learn compatible estimator
* `X`: feature matrix
* `y`: target vector

### `evaluate(view="all", plot=False)`

* `view`: `"executive"`, `"technical"`, `"details"`, `"all"` or custom list
* `plot`: generates graphs when `True`

